[
    {
        "text": "When I met Michael, I was 14 years old, and I knew that he was gonna be my boyfriend.",
        "startTime": 27797,
        "endTime": 34411,
        "slowStartTime": 41846,
        "slowEndTime": 51841
    },
    {
        "text": "We got married when I was 19, and we were both kids.",
        "startTime": 35658,
        "endTime": 39362,
        "slowStartTime": 53637,
        "slowEndTime": 59268
    },
    {
        "text": "We really didn't know what next.",
        "startTime": 39486,
        "endTime": 41337,
        "slowStartTime": 59379,
        "slowEndTime": 62231
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, get married and now what?",
        "startTime": 41555,
        "endTime": 43557,
        "slowStartTime": 62482,
        "slowEndTime": 65560
    },
    {
        "text": "When we were divorced, I remember the kids telling me...",
        "startTime": 44681,
        "endTime": 48403,
        "slowStartTime": 67171,
        "slowEndTime": 72830
    },
    {
        "text": "...that their father confided in them with a secret.",
        "startTime": 48621,
        "endTime": 51332,
        "slowStartTime": 73082,
        "slowEndTime": 77223
    },
    {
        "text": "And they said, \"Well, daddy still loves you.\"",
        "startTime": 52016,
        "endTime": 53931,
        "slowStartTime": 78174,
        "slowEndTime": 81122
    },
    {
        "text": "He doesn't want us to tell you.",
        "startTime": 54498,
        "endTime": 55940,
        "slowStartTime": 81897,
        "slowEndTime": 84135
    },
    {
        "text": "And I said, \"Well, I know.\"",
        "startTime": 57062,
        "endTime": 58254,
        "slowStartTime": 85743,
        "slowEndTime": 87606
    },
    {
        "text": "And I love him, too, but Mommy and Daddy have gone their separate ways.",
        "startTime": 58407,
        "endTime": 63070,
        "slowStartTime": 87761,
        "slowEndTime": 94830
    },
    {
        "text": "But we'll always be a family, and we'll always be your mom and dad.",
        "startTime": 63179,
        "endTime": 65960,
        "slowStartTime": 94918,
        "slowEndTime": 99165
    },
    {
        "text": "On 9/11, I remember getting up to take my daughter.",
        "startTime": 67467,
        "endTime": 72159,
        "slowStartTime": 101350,
        "slowEndTime": 108463
    },
    {
        "text": "She had a doctor's appointment, so my daughter was home.",
        "startTime": 72247,
        "endTime": 74623,
        "slowStartTime": 108520,
        "slowEndTime": 112159
    },
    {
        "text": "At 9:04, I got a phone call and it was Michael, and he was calling from the 103rd floor.",
        "startTime": 75155,
        "endTime": 83130,
        "slowStartTime": 112883,
        "slowEndTime": 124920
    },
    {
        "text": "And the first thing that he said was, \"I'm calling to say goodbye.\"",
        "startTime": 83989,
        "endTime": 88147,
        "slowStartTime": 126134,
        "slowEndTime": 132445
    },
    {
        "text": "And I said, \"Why? Where are you going?\"",
        "startTime": 88781,
        "endTime": 90961,
        "slowStartTime": 133322,
        "slowEndTime": 136666
    },
    {
        "text": "And he said, \"Well, I'm in the building that was just hit by a plane.\"",
        "startTime": 91596,
        "endTime": 95527,
        "slowStartTime": 137544,
        "slowEndTime": 143516
    },
    {
        "text": "He just wanted to tell me how much he loved the children.",
        "startTime": 97017,
        "endTime": 99999,
        "slowStartTime": 145675,
        "slowEndTime": 150224
    },
    {
        "text": "And he says, \"You know, I also want to tell you that I always loved you.\"",
        "startTime": 100836,
        "endTime": 108155,
        "slowStartTime": 151404,
        "slowEndTime": 162457
    },
    {
        "text": "And I said, \"I know, the kids told me.\"",
        "startTime": 108983,
        "endTime": 111735,
        "slowStartTime": 163624,
        "slowEndTime": 167827
    },
    {
        "text": "And my daughter was there, and she saw me becoming a little hysterical.",
        "startTime": 113165,
        "endTime": 119289,
        "slowStartTime": 169897,
        "slowEndTime": 179158
    },
    {
        "text": "And I didn't know whether to put her on because I didn't know how he would react.",
        "startTime": 119379,
        "endTime": 124723,
        "slowStartTime": 179218,
        "slowEndTime": 187310
    },
    {
        "text": "He thought she was at school.",
        "startTime": 124795,
        "endTime": 127295,
        "slowStartTime": 187343,
        "slowEndTime": 191168
    },
    {
        "text": "It just really breaks my heart that he's not here for them.",
        "startTime": 131897,
        "endTime": 135085,
        "slowStartTime": 197996,
        "slowEndTime": 202852
    },
    {
        "text": "It's like the only thing on his mind was to tell the kids that he loved them.",
        "startTime": 136939,
        "endTime": 141473,
        "slowStartTime": 205706,
        "slowEndTime": 211931
    },
    {
        "text": "And the thing is, is that my two children look just like him.",
        "startTime": 143270,
        "endTime": 146755,
        "slowStartTime": 215055,
        "slowEndTime": 220358
    },
    {
        "text": "And they talk like him, and they joke like him.",
        "startTime": 147538,
        "endTime": 151553,
        "slowStartTime": 221457,
        "slowEndTime": 227554
    },
    {
        "text": "So, it's like he's there.",
        "startTime": 153458,
        "endTime": 155250,
        "slowStartTime": 230337,
        "slowEndTime": 233100
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, I see him in them every day.",
        "startTime": 155352,
        "endTime": 157557,
        "slowStartTime": 233178,
        "slowEndTime": 236560
    },
    {
        "text": "And as much as he used to drive me crazy, he was my family and my best friend.",
        "startTime": 158895,
        "endTime": 167529,
        "slowStartTime": 238493,
        "slowEndTime": 251519
    }
]